            <title>[LU-8939] nodemap: remove deprecated lproc files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8939</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Before the MGS was able to transfer the nodemap configuration to the MDSes and OSSes, people had to use lproc interfaces in order to load the configuration. Now that the MGS can pass the configuration to the servers, these administrative lproc interfaces should be removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
